{"tid":963403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女究竟當我係咩?","createTime":"2018-12-31T14:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T15:20:13.000Z","uid":152224,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"456eedc0914813de3caa5732bb255b1a47a6daca","tid":963403,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"我同條女喺9月果陣返part time識嘅<br />\n大家都係大學生 (唔同U)<br />\n我地覺得大家都好夾 <br />\n於是就不斷單獨約會 (&gt;10次）<br />\n幾乎日日見<br />\n<br />\n每次食飯都係由我埋單<br />\n而且食d嘢唔平 （$100-1000）<br />\n雖然佢家境好過我好多 （住半山）<br />\n但男人埋單可以加下分<br />\n增加對方好感都值嘅<br />\n另外我每星期都會送d禮物比佢<br />\n<br />\n佢主動過我好多 (可能我係A0冇經驗）<br />\n每次都係佢約我出街<br />\n而且傾計佢都會主動搵下新話題<br />\n又話對我有好感<br />\n令我以為佢中意我<br />\n<br />\n直到聖誕, 我終於同佢表白<br />\n我送咗份好貴重嘅聖誕禮物比佢 (但佢竟然冇比我）<br />\n佢表情好開心<br />\n佢話相處多陣先<br />\n2019前會比答覆我 （99%有機咁）<br />\n<br />\n直到今日除夕, 佢用WhatsApp 拒絕咗我<br />\n仲話以後唔好見<br />\n因為佢已經有咗男朋友 (其實係上一個ex, 散咗一年,今日復合返, 之前係條仔飛佢)<br />\n條仔仲要係MK仔黎<br />\n中學畢業冇再讀書<br />\n做飲食行業得11k<br />\n仲要係住劏房<br />\n<br />\n條女仲send同佢食貴嘢d相比我<br />\n重點係條女埋單tim (同我食係未拎過銀包出黎）<br />\n仲話雖然條仔窮<br />\n但會養埋佢一世<br />\n仲同我講今晚會一齊同床瞓住跨年<br />\n<br />\n雖然我身高外貌可能及唔上條MK仔<br />\n但人品,性格,學歷,家境係屌打佢<br />\n都會落得如此下場...<br />\n仲要朋友都唔想同我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我total用咗5皮黎溝佢 （對學生哥黎講真係好多下）<br />\n但佢而家用我d錢去養第二條仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9c25f1bd6523a1448f994bced95c8acb41e335","tid":963403,"uid":69484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"ced5afdbf3f5c17a496e820d641771f2f4c9ad1f","tid":963403,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"5皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26bfa76aff28cc6f97d1bbfab2b475aba3053f4","tid":963403,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"5皮 我勸你當扔咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e475ef60b459c1a67926f0340a982fa21a74707","tid":963403,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"atm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2008306b989e7109846639aebbea30b50bb0db","tid":963403,"uid":54754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2189f1af60291d80459165a92f8c305732b39a2f","tid":963403,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"d370545a8769e0dcc3fd5e2ad7564bff0bd8df75","tid":963403,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"同佢close 咗三個月都無發現佢仲留戀ex，你都好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 又食又拎嘅女人就算啦，搵過個肯AA 㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc59139483399f282142eb385c2323a0abeb27b1","tid":963403,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"人哋住半山點會介意對方家境差（除咗老竇老母介意）<br />\n就算差過你佢都養得起有餘啦<br />\n咩用你啲錢貼仔真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嗰5萬分分鐘係人哋一個月零用咋"},{"pid":"30e26aa95d56ff6a4367220289562bf56f86fc7d","tid":963403,"uid":164930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:38:45.000Z","msg":"求其你地返咩pt 識嫁  你又講到佢咁好家境"},{"pid":"2ef3f3559e690e9e08a1bf019c02e7971c5f8d8d","tid":963403,"uid":164930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e26aa95d56ff6a4367220289562bf56f86fc7d","tid":963403,"uid":164930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:38:45.000Z","msg":"求其你地返咩pt 識嫁  你又講到